<div type="content"><ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Wyrich, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                            <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Glanczen, ewrs
                            <expan>dien<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, und <expan>Bercht<ex>old</ex></expan>
                        Helmsmids und Andres Laybers <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>grichtschreib<ex>er</ex></expan> besant und befolhen, in
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> grichtsbuch
                            <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu suchen; der hat
                                <expan>darinn<ex>en</ex></expan> gefunden, daz die
                                <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>Bercht<ex>old</ex></expan> Helmsmid und
                            <expan>Andr<ex>es</ex></expan> Layber <add>mit
                                <expan>gesampt<ex>er</ex></expan></add>
<add>hant</add>
<app>
<note>&gt;<q type="date">an sand Blasien tag <add>nach Crists
                                        gebürt</add> xiiii<hi rend="sup">c</hi> und xii jare
                                            <expan>nehstv<ex>er</ex>gang<ex>en</ex></expan></q>03.08.1412</note>
</app> Mertein <expan>Hall<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>selig<ex>en</ex></expan>, Hannsen <expan>Hübn<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Glancze<ex>n</ex></expan> und etwievil <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>p<ex>er</ex>sonen</expan>, iren <expan>schuldig<ex>er</ex>n</expan>,
                                <expan>yegliche<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>sum<ex>m</ex>e</expan> schulde und mit na[men] dem
                                <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Glancze<ex>n</ex></expan> c und lx <expan>r<ex>einisch</ex></expan>
<expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> in <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> grichtsbuch
                        be[kannt] und darauf gesworen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                                <expan>yegliche<ex>m</ex></expan> irem
                            <expan>schuldig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> achtteils<app>
<note><gap reason="damaged"/></note>
</app> schulde in der <expan>nehstkünftig<ex>en</ex></expan> herbstmess zu
                                <expan>Frankf<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> darnach zu geb[en] und darnach all
                        herbstmess <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>sechczehend<ex>en</ex></expan> teil der schulde zu beczaln, alslank
                        uncz die <expan>schuldig<ex>er</ex></expan> beczalt
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. Wie <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> die
                        sache <expan>seidh<ex>er</ex></expan> gehandelt und
                            <expan>ergang<ex>en</ex></expan> sey, da ist uns niht
                                <expan>wissenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> von. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>i<ex>n</ex></expan> festo pasche. </ab></div>
<div type="cedula">
<ab>Cettula <expan>int<ex>er</ex>clusa</expan>: Lieber
                            <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Wyrich, als ir uns
                            <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt, der sache grichtsbrief zu
                                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, süllt ir wissen, daz die sache seid
                        der zeit der <expan>erste<ex>n</ex></expan> bekentnuss in
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> grichtsbuch niht
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>new[ert] </expan>
<expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> ist. Und ist <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        form niht, was <expan>ynn<ex>er</ex></expan> jars frist niht
                        v<ex>er</ex>n[ewrt] wirdt, daz wir <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>grichtsbr<ex>ief</ex></expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Das wellet in gut <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        [uns] <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan>. </ab>
</div>
